=head1 DESCRIPTION

Filters configuration recorders by recording scope.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 FilterName => Str

The name of the type of filter. Currently, only C<recordingScope> is
supported.


=head2 FilterValue => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The value of the filter. For C<recordingScope>, valid values include:
C<INTERNAL> and C<PAID>.

C<INTERNAL> indicates that the ConfigurationItems
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/config/latest/APIReference/API_ConfigurationItem.html)
in scope for the configuration recorder are recorded for free.

C<PAID> indicates that the ConfigurationItems
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/config/latest/APIReference/API_ConfigurationItem.html)
in scope for the configuration recorder impact the costs to your bill.



